column2: "Hey, partner. This planet is really hot. Just walking around is making me tired."
"The person I'm looking for hasn't turned up, but that's to be expected."
"It's not like this undeveloped planet has a high probability of success in the first place."
"But a while ago I did see a small little shadow at the end of the desert."
"It was too small to be a person's shadow so I wonder what I could have been..."
"Ah, it's too hot to think. I'm going to head back and cool off."
